headline.main: Late and Interesting From Mexico--Loss of the Amercian Bark Avalanche, & c.

docs.lead_paragraph: By the arrival of the steamship Orizava we have dates from Mexico to the 4th inst. The American bark Avalanche foundered at sen, when about seventy-five miles from Vera Cruz. The Captain and crew were saved.

docs.lead_paragraph: Our weather is cool and Fall-like, although we have not yet had frost, which we anticipate soon. The yellow fever seems to be pretty well over, although we yet have an occasional death.
